*************************************************
mail program is an erlang application but event handler is not implemented.

To start the mail server run 

1> application:start(mail).
2> mail:connect("erlang.arduino@gmail.com","raptor2012").
3> mail:send_mail("Subject:Test message ","Test message.\nrow1.\nrow2", "joakim.leche@gmail.com").

